org.eclipse.viatra.cep.vepl.vepl

Interface ComplexEventExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Atom
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AtomImpl, ComplexEventExpressionImpl

    public interface ComplexEventExpression
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Complex Event Expression'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Left
    • Right
    • Multiplicity
    • Timewindow
    See Also:
    VeplPackage.getComplexEventExpression()
